config EXYNOS1280_TMU
	tristate "Samsung Exynos 1280 TMU thermal driver"
	depends on OF
	depends on THERMAL
	default y
	help
	  Thermal Management Unit driver for Samsung Exynos 1280 (s5e8825).
	  Uses the standard Linux thermal subsystem. Monitors CPU clusters,
	  GPU, and ISP temperatures.
